<H1>Welcome to AAPD Online!</H1>
<H2><I>Healthy Smiles - Healthy Children</I></H2>
<H4>The American Academy of Pediatric Dentistry is the professional organization<BR>whose dentist members are specially trained to provide both primary and<BR>comprehensive preventive and therapeutic oral health care for infants,<BR>children, adolescents, and patients with special health care needs.</H4>
<H5><I>Updated: March 11, 1996</I></H5><BR>
